metadata.description:
Somewhere in a faraway, there is a forest that shrouded in a dark. In its depth, under a shade of fragrant trees, there is a thicket full of fantastic plants, alive mushrooms, flourishing flowers and of course, maiden nymphs.  
They dance and sing their beautiful songs, that seep through distant distances. If you are very lucky to hear their voices from afar, this divine and inexpressible tune will stick in your mind till the end of your days.
